It does not according to gender predictable and apprehended (summary biographical, life and work), but in seeking something similar to the core of ignition of character created.
The trip is exciting and Vincent spares neither fear nor illuminations.
Delicious pleasure, this book is also an invitation moving to readings and reviews.
